{"lemma":"بَصِير","slug":"بَصِير","root":"ب.ص.ر","root_slug":"ب-ص-ر","root_link":"/words/roots/ب-ص-ر","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"بَصِير","root":"بصر","pos":"N","occurrence_count":51},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["adj"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":4},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n2651"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%A8%D9%8E%D8%B5%D9%90%D9%8A%D8%B1"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"adj","gloss":"well-seeing; having eyesight, seeing, sighted"},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"clairvoyant, observant, perspicacious","tags":["figuratively"]},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"well-versed, conversant, informed","tags":["figuratively"]},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"blind","tags":["rare"]}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":["/ba.sˤiːr/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n2651","headword_ar":"بَصِيرٌ","root":"bSr","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Seeing; i. q."},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"muboSirN","text_ar":"مُبْصِرٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (M, K;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"contr. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DariyrN","text_ar":"ضَرِيرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S:) of the measure"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faEiylN","text_ar":"فَعِيلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"in the sense of the measure"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mufoEilN","text_ar":"مُفْعِلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (M,) or of the measure"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faAEilN","text_ar":"فَاعِلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e. ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baASirN","text_ar":"بَاصِرٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"] : (TA:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"buSaraA='u","text_ar":"بُصَرَا=ءُ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (M, K.) One says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_in~ahu labaSiyrN biAlEayonayoni","text_ar":"اـِنَّهُ لَبَصِيرٌ بِالعَيْنَيْنِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Verily he is one who sees with the two eyes."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Lh, M.) [Hence,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlbaSiyru","text_ar":"البَصِيرُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", as a name of God,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The All-seeing; He who sees all things, both what are apparent thereof and what are occult, without any organ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of vision"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The dog;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M;) as also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^abuw baSiyrK","text_ar":"اَبُو بَصِيرٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (Msb:) because it is one of the most sharp-sighted of animals. (M.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Endowed with mental perception;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(B;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"knowing; skilful; possessing understanding, intelligence,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"skill:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, M, A, Msb, K:) pl. as above. (A.) One says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^anaA baSiyrN bihi","text_ar":"اَنَا بَصِيرٌ بِهِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I am knowing in it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"respecting it."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_in~ahu labaSiyrN biAlA^a$oyaA='i","text_ar":"اـِنَّهُ لَبَصِيرٌ بِالاَشْيَا=ءِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Verily he is knowing,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"skilful, in things."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Lh, M.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rajulN baSiyrN biAlEilomi","text_ar":"رَجُلٌ بَصِيرٌ بِالعِلْمِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A man knowing,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"skilful, in science."},{"kind":"text","text":"(M.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"huwa mina AlbuSaraA='i biAlit~jaArapi","text_ar":"هُوَ مِنَ البُصَرَا=ءِ بِالِتّجَارَةِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He is of those who are knowing,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"skilful, in commerce."},{"kind":"text","text":"(A.) ―         -b3-  It is also an epithet applied to A"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"blind"},{"kind":"text","text":"man; (A'Obeyd, M, B;) and so"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^abuw baSiyrK","text_ar":"اَبُو بَصِيرٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (TA in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ewr","text_ar":"عور"},{"kind":"text","text":":) so applied as meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"endowed with mental perception;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(B;) or as meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a believer;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A'Obeyd, M;) or as an epithet of good omen: (M:) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^abuw baSiyrK","text_ar":"اَبُو بَصِيرٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is used as meaning"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlA^aEo$aY","text_ar":"الاَعْشَى"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the weaksighted,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.,] for this last reason. (M.)       -A2-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baSiyrapN","text_ar":"بَصِيرَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":["S","M","TA","Msb","A","K"]}]}}